*.gz

# Intentional exception: gate-passing signed DE long table (task A extract).
# Committed gzipped because the uncompressed CSV (~130MB) exceeds GitHub's
# 100MB hard file-size limit; gzip brings it to ~48MB. See
# docs/mvp-research/TASK_A_GB10_HANDOFF.md for provenance.
!metadata/suppl_tables/gate_passing_signed_DE.suppl_table.csv.gz

# Transient runtime target-card caches produced by the target_card_api service.
# Keep the intentional _evidence seed snapshots and any already-tracked demo
# datasets tracked; ignore new per-run dataset/import dirs so test/runtime
# artifacts do not get committed.
sources/target_tool_cache/usr_*/
sources/target_tool_cache/imports/*/
sources/target_tool_cache/[0-9a-f]*-[0-9a-f]*/

# Keep the committed explainer site (overrides **/*.html above)
!docs/explainer/index.html

# Isolated ML exploration space (src/10_ml_perturbation_prediction/README.md):
# `data/` is a local feature-cache derived from metadata/suppl_tables/, safe to
# rebuild, not provenance. `results/` (benchmark reports) IS committed.
src/10_ml_perturbation_prediction/data/*
!src/10_ml_perturbation_prediction/data/.gitkeep
src/10_ml_perturbation_prediction/.venv_ml/

# Keep the committed researcher-guide site (overrides **/*.html above)
!docs/researcher_guide/index.html
